70
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,680
Jangan cari aku!

71
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,120
Jangan.

72
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,840
Jangan!

73
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,159
