158
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,639
Mao Buyu.

159
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,600
Ternyata kau demi dia...

160
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,720
Kak Wushuang.

161
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,199
Aku khawatir kau tidak akan bisa
mengakhiri hal ini pada akhirnya.

162
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:49,800
Jika kau benar-benar mengkhawatirkanku,
seharusnya kau tidak menghalangiku.

163
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,079
Lakukan!

164
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,279
Buyu!

165
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,360
-Yu.
-Buyu!

166
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,319
Yu!

167
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,720
